text: It's laughable isn't it, that score.

Oh my, how kind.
Thank you.

...But you know, Fuyu won't simply accept
words like that at face value.

Straightforward honesty won't be accepted.
Something careful crafted to be liked won't reach...
It really is an absurd world, isn't it.
Next time I'll definitely take down our opposition.

That score, whether or not you want to accept that,
Fuyuko's performance was the best.

Truthfully, it was good enough to
destroy this absurd world.

─Fufu, you're such a dummy.
It clearly didn't destroy it.
